::KitKat::
She woke up and looked over at the chamber.  Drilbit wasn't in it 
anymore.  She opened her link,"Drillbit? Where are you?" She still 
had pain and didn't want to really move around a whole lot yet.

Feline::
She kissed HotRod. "Do you think that a lucky kitty like me would 
ever say no to a bot like you?" She smiled and kissed him again.
